eas_text: A CIVIL AUTHORITY HAS ISSUED A REQUIRED MONTHLY TEST FOR THE FOLLOWING COUNTIES/AREAS: Clallam, WA; AT 03:46 PM ON NOV 07, 2025 EFFECTIVE UNTIL 06:46 PM. MESSAGE FROM WSLF/CAP.
extra_text:
This is a test. This is only a test of the Emergency Alert System in Clallam County issued by Clallam County Emergency Management.
